The key elements of a CSCW system are actor, activity, resources and
tools. Every CSCW system is designed using these elements. A groupware
application provides the above mentioned interactions. All five of them are
essential for a good collaborative system. The project defines these
interactions in the scenarios of local as well as remote collaboration.
Further from the primary studies a tentative timeline of an architectural
project was prepared to identify the collaborations happening during the
project. A detailed study of Building Information Technology (BIM) was also
done as the product was desingned in a way they it can be used as an
extention of BIM rather than a stand alone product. Based on the study
ideation was done on the possible scenarios.
